text: The 2009 Texas State Bobcats football team represented Texas State University–San Marcos in the 2009 NCAA Division I FCS football season. The Bobcats led by third year head coach Brad Wright, played their home games at Bobcat Stadium as a member of the Southland Conference. They finished the season with a record of seven wins and four losses (7-4, 5-2 Southland). ==Schedule== https://s3.amazonaws.com/sidearm.sites/txstate.sidearmsports.com/documents/2018/8/23/2018_Texas_State_Football_Media_Guide.pdf ==References== Texas State Category:Texas State Bobcats football seasons Texas State
